name: tapable-tracer
description: Trace the connections and flows between tapable hooks.

scripts.build: yarn build:clean && yarn build::types && yarn build::cjs && yarn build::esm && yarn exports:update
scripts.build::types: tsc --project ./tsconfig.output.types.json && node -e "console.log('Successfully compiled source files for dts format with tsc.')"
scripts.exports:update: export-map-generator generate && node -e "console.log('Successfully updated package exports.')"
